## ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
## Smart Tourism Samosir — API Test File
## ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

## Global Variables
@baseurl=http://127.0.0.1:5000

## Setelah login, copy token ke sini:
@token=PASTE_TOKEN_DI_SINI

## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
## HEALTH CHECK
## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseurl}}/
###

## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
## AUTH
## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Login Admin
# @name LoginAdmin
POST {{baseurl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}
###

## Login Tester
# @name LoginTester
POST {{baseurl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tester",
  "password": "tester123"
}
###

## Login — Password Salah (expect 401)
POST {{baseurl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "salah"
}
###

## Profil User yang Sedang Login
GET {{baseurl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
## TOURIST SPOTS
## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Get Semua Tempat Wisata (paginasi)
GET {{baseurl}}/spots?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Filter by Kategori
GET {{baseurl}}/spots?category=Alam
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Filter by Kategori + Search
GET {{baseurl}}/spots?category=Budaya&search=simanindo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Get Daftar Kategori
GET {{baseurl}}/spots/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Detail Tempat Wisata (id=1)
GET {{baseurl}}/spots/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Tanpa Token — Harus 401
GET {{baseurl}}/spots
###

## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
## AI REKOMENDASI WISATA
## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Generate Rekomendasi
# @name GenerateRekomendasi
POST {{baseurl}}/recommendations/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interest": "wisata alam dan petualangan outdoor",
  "budget": "medium",
  "duration": 3
}
###

## Generate Rekomendasi Kuliner
POST {{baseurl}}/recommendations/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interest": "wisata kuliner dan budaya Batak"
}
###

## Riwayat Rekomendasi
GET {{baseurl}}/recommendations?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Detail Rekomendasi (id=1)
GET {{baseurl}}/recommendations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Hapus Rekomendasi (id=1)
DELETE {{baseurl}}/recommendations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
## AI ITINERARY PERJALANAN
## ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Generate Itinerary 3 Hari — Keluarga
# @name GenerateItinerary
POST {{baseurl}}/itineraries/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "budaya dan kuliner Batak",
  "duration_days": 3,
  "budget": "medium",
  "group_type": "family"
}
###

## Generate Itinerary 2 Hari — Solo Backpacker
POST {{baseurl}}/itineraries/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "alam dan petualangan",
  "duration_days": 2,
  "budget": "low",
  "group_type": "solo"
}
###

## Generate Itinerary — Validasi Error (duration_days > 7)
POST {{baseurl}}/itineraries/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "liburan panjang",
  "duration_days": 10,
  "budget": "high",
  "group_type": "couple"
}
###

## Riwayat Itinerary
GET {{baseurl}}/itineraries?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Detail Itinerary (id=1)
GET {{baseurl}}/itineraries/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

## Hapus Itinerary (id=1)
DELETE {{baseurl}}/itineraries/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###
